org.wise.vle.domain.annotation

Class Annotation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wise.vle.domain.PersistableDomain
      • org.wise.vle.domain.annotation.Annotation

  • @Entity
public class Annotation
extends PersistableDomain
    Domain representing Annotation. Annotations are what users annotate on other user's work, such as Comments, Scores, Flags.
    Author:
    Hiroki Terashima
